info.name: enact-SO
info.summary: ENACT is the first tissue-agnostic pipeline that integrates advanced cell segmentation with Visium HD transcriptomics data to infer cell types across whole tissue sections. This pipeline incorporates novel bin-to-cell assignment methods, enhancing the accuracy of single-cell transcript estimates.
